      <title>荷兰在埃因霍温投资 25 亿欧元，以保持 ASML 的地位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/dutch-invest-2-5-billion-in-eindhoven-area-to-keep-asml-on-side</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在科技巨头 ASML Holding NV 威胁要向海外扩张后，荷兰政府将斥资 25 亿欧元（27 亿美元）用于埃因霍温地区的基础设施和教育项目。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/dutch-invest-2-5-billion-in-eindhoven-area-to-keep-asml-on-side</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 16:34:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
